                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Personally, I think that it was a hoax.  If it is not a hoax,the measures taken by SoE have started to work.
<br />

<br />
Prices did rise on 7th Hammer.  Some items that I was looking for doubled in price (just as I was earning the plat to afford them, of course).  This could have been the result of purchased plat.  It could also have been the result of price gougers, or it could have been panic caused by a hoax.
<br />

<br />
The prices of those items is falling again.  It is not back down to where it was, but it is getting there.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Sandiilu Sommerbreeze
