                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Then consider the following scenario.
<br />

<br />
SOE have "banned or deleted hundreds of acounts/charactors". These charactors I assume were the ones spending infinte platinum to buy uber items. These items have now been deleted..... but the platinum is still in the system. Hence we are left with a system that is still flooded with platinum but is missing many of the top end items (they were deleted). An obvious conclusion is that the prices of the remaining high end items will be bid up even further as all that platinum tries to find homes. This will eventually correct when people farm/obtain many of these items again but short term we could continue to see inflation of prices for high end items.
<br />

<br />
Satikkine</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
